title: Growing a chemical snake that looks like a turd

media:group.media:title: Growing a chemical snake that looks like a turd
media:group.media:description:
This is a new type of video style that we have decided to try. It is a lot more casual and it involves my brother and our friend (the camera guy). In this one, we burned calcium gluconate pills to make a weird snake thing, and it was something that I wanted to do for a while.

Waste/safety info: https://nile.red/s/Calcium-Gluconate-Snake.pdf
